quran[4]{c,v,t,f}:
  5,10,"Àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́, tí wọ́n sì pe àwọn āyah Wa ní irọ́, àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ní èrò inú iná Jẹhīm.",""
  5,11,"Ẹ̀yin tí ẹ gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, ẹ rántí ìdẹ̀ra tí Allāhu ṣe fún yín; nígbà tí ìjọ kan gbèrò látinawọ́ ìjà si yín, (Allāhu) sì kó wọn lọ́wọ́ rọ̀ fún yín. Ẹ bẹ̀rù Allāhu. Àti pé Allāhu ni kí àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo gbáralé.",""
  5,12,"Dájúdájú Allāhu gba àdéhùn lọ́wọ́ àwọn ọmọ ’Isrọ̄’īl. A sì gbé ìjòyè méjìlá dìde nínú wọn. Allāhu sì sọ (fún wọn) pé: “Dájúdájú Mò ń bẹ pẹ̀lú yín, tí ẹ bá ń kírun, tí ẹ̀ bá ń yọ Zakāh, tí ẹ bá gba àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ Mi gbọ́, tí ẹ ràn wọ́n lọ́wọ́, tí ẹ sì yá Allāhu ní dúkìá tó dára. Dájúdájú Mo máa pa àwọn àṣìṣe yín rẹ́. Dájúdájú Mo máa mu yín wọ inú àwọn Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra kan, tí àwọn odò ń ṣàn ní ìsàlẹ̀ rẹ̀. Àmọ́ ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá ṣàì gbàgbọ́ lẹ́yìn ìyẹn nínú yín, ó kúkú ti ṣìnà kúrò lójú ọ̀nà tààrà.”",""
  5,13,"Nítorí yíyẹ̀ tí wọ́n fúnra wọn yẹ àdéhùn wọn ni A fi ṣẹ́bi lé wọn. A sì mú ọkàn wọn le koko (nítorí pé), wọ́n ń gbé àwọn ọ̀rọ̀ kúrò ní àwọn àyè rẹ̀, wọ́n sì gbàgbé ìpín kan nínúoore tí A rán wọn létí rẹ̀. O ò níí yé rí oníjàǹbá láààrin wọn àfi díẹ̀ nínú wọn. Nítorí náà, ṣe àmójúkúrò fún wọn, kí o sì foríjìn wọ́n. Dájúdájú Allāhu fẹ́ràn àwọn olùṣe-rere.",""
